@SimpleApp.LogServer_HostAddress = http://localhost:5180

### Ingest a log entry
POST {{SimpleApp.LogServer_HostAddress}}/api/logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Welcome email stub: sending welcome to test@example.com",
  "level": "INFO",
  "service": "simpleapp",
  "source": "UserEventConsumer",
  "hostname": "localhost",
  "tags": "env:development",
  "attributes": {
    "userId": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6",
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "event": "UserCreated"
  }
}

###

### Query all logs
GET {{SimpleApp.LogServer_HostAddress}}/api/logs
Accept: application/json

###

### Query logs by level
GET {{SimpleApp.LogServer_HostAddress}}/api/logs?level=INFO&page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

###

### Query logs by service
GET {{SimpleApp.LogServer_HostAddress}}/api/logs?service=simpleapp
Accept: application/json

###

### Query logs by date range
GET {{SimpleApp.LogServer_HostAddress}}/api/logs?from=2026-01-01T00:00:00Z&to=2026-12-31T23:59:59Z
Accept: application/json

###

### Get log stats
GET {{SimpleApp.LogServer_HostAddress}}/api/logs/stats
Accept: application/json

###
